Flask-Flarf Changelog
========================

Version 0.0.5
-------------

Released September 12th 2013

- determine param type/function on init as partial function and set to take only
  request on filter run
- regex for filter_on & filter_pass

Version 0.0.4
-------------

Released September 10th 2013

- simplification of filter/filtered to one filter placed on g
- params are set as an ordered dict in filter(ordered dict of partial methods based on inference at init)
- allow for specifying methods on class as a filter param using "get_(paramname)" in subclassed filter 
- context prcessor based on filter tag


Version 0.0.3
-------------

Released June 20th 2013

- basic context processor(flarf_ctx) that retrieves by filter tag


Version 0.0.2
-------------

Released June 6th 2013

- change from 'preprocessor' to 'filter' terminology in variables
- filter intialization and ordering
- filters can get a simple parameter or run a function over request
- effective testing 


Version 0.0.1
-------------

Released May 24th 2013

- first working version as an extension, from previous blueprint code


Version 0.0.0
-------------

Released May 21st 2013

- project initialization and basic setup
